Arch Linux Midfingr Edition

ISO refresh June 2016

- lightdm login manager replaces lxdm
- lightdm settings manager for customizing the login screen
- volumeicon replaces volwheel
- included chrome and chromium flags for optimal speed and safety
- Documentation expanded to include Nvidia Libraries and configuration
- efitools replace prebootloader # as per Arch Linux packages
- networkmanager-dispatcher-ntpd # sync computer time using the network time protocol

ISO refresh March 2016

- xfce4 desktop environment
- menu-driven installer by Carl Duff updated to v2.2
- removed gnome application integration
- removed pacmac-aur
- expanded Documentation to include Virtualbox services when running as Guest
- chromium avatars for use with mugshot